      "body" : "Deterministic wallets (https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0032.mediawiki) would allow for this .From one seed an infinite number of keys can be generated, so if you don't care about metadata you can make a backup once and use it to restore from forever.\r\n\r\nThere is a long-standing open issue to implement, see #3250.\r\n\r\nSome other wallets such as Electrum already have this feature.\r\n",
